2.4 Using URL

API URL

Re-Stat API: https://qiita.com/nozma/items/f88f5cc60ab63461deae

library(httr)
#  ID 
appid <- appId # " ID"

#  ID 
statsDataId <- "0003445078"

# 
response <- GET(url = "http://api.e-stat.go.jp/rest/3.0/app/getSimpleStatsData",
                 query = list(appId = appid,
                              statsDataId = statsDataId,
                              metaGetFlg = "Y",
                              cntGetFlg = "N",
                              explanationGetFlg = "Y",
                              annotationGetFlg = "Y",
                              sectionHeaderFlg = "1",
                              replaceSpChars = "0"))
glimpse(response)
